        <item>
            <title>Rubien 0.1.2</title>
            <description><![CDATA[Reader: the Clipped and Live tabs are now a single Clip tab with a
  Refresh button, plus a new Original tab that shows the live web page. Notion pages now clip with
   code blocks, math, images, toggles, and callouts preserved. Math in clipped articles keeps its
  color. Annotation popovers no longer clip at the right edge of the window.]]></description>
